text:
Public Notice The Port of Brookings Harbor Board of ad date: 10/24/2015 
The Port of Brookings Harbor Board of Commissioners has scheduled the following meeting: Wednesday - October 28th, 2015 - 3:00 PM Commissioners' Executive Session per ORS 192.660(2)(g): To discuss Personnel Issues. The meeting will take place in the Port Office, 16340 Lower Harbor Rd Suite 103, Brookings, OR 97415. Publish October 24, 2015
